{"pr_number": 9420, "pr_title": "KAFKA-10604: The StreamsConfig.STATE_DIR_CONFIG's default value does not reflect the JVM parameter or OS-specific settings", "pr_createdAt": "2020-10-13T08:09:41Z", "pr_url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/9420", "timeline": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1Mjk5NDk4MQ==", "url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/9420#discussion_r552994981", "bodyText": "Thanks for this @dongjinleekr !\nIt's kind of a bummer that we actually create this file while defining the configurations, since it results in leaking temp directories, even if users set this config to a different value.\nDo you think we can do this in a lazy fashion?", "author": "vvcephei", "createdAt": "2021-01-06T22:24:35Z", "path": "streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/StreamsConfig.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -602,7 +603,7 @@\n                     REPLICATION_FACTOR_DOC)\n             .define(STATE_DIR_CONFIG,\n                     Type.STRING,\n-                    \"/tmp/kafka-streams\",\n+                    Utils.getTempDir().resolve(\"kafka-streams\").toAbsolutePath().toString(),", "originalCommit": "7b474cbe848282652396ff6d030047df63b5efd0", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1MzAxMDA0OQ==", "url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/9420#discussion_r553010049", "bodyText": "Good point John. Maybe we should just use System.getProperty(\"java.io.tmpdir\") here?\nWe have already code in place in StateDirectory constructor to create the ./kafka-streams sub-directory. Might be good enough without any additional changes?", "author": "mjsax", "createdAt": "2021-01-06T23:08:28Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1Mjk5NDk4MQ=="}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1MzM1NTM5OQ==", "url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/9420#discussion_r553355399", "bodyText": "@vvcephei @mjsax Totally agree. Since I am now finalizing KAFKA-8403 now, I will fix this with a integration test after that. \ud83d\ude4f", "author": "dongjinleekr", "createdAt": "2021-01-07T14:19:41Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDU1Mjk5NDk4MQ=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "f89588f22ed33436a5fa89b2b337fce03f1743ca", "url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/commit/f89588f22ed33436a5fa89b2b337fce03f1743ca", "message": "Use System.getProperty(\"java.io.tmpdir\") instead of constant '/tmp'", "committedDate": "2021-01-18T08:07:35Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "612cbafeb0b1b1120db884beb68844bad19f8adc", "url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/commit/612cbafeb0b1b1120db884beb68844bad19f8adc", "message": "Use System.getProperty(\"java.io.tmpdir\") instead of constant '/tmp'", "committedDate": "2021-01-28T04:15:42Z", "type": "commit"}, {"oid": "612cbafeb0b1b1120db884beb68844bad19f8adc", "url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/commit/612cbafeb0b1b1120db884beb68844bad19f8adc", "message": "Use System.getProperty(\"java.io.tmpdir\") instead of constant '/tmp'", "committedDate": "2021-01-28T04:15:42Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "0ba0a4735ecc71d9c335d7ecaffcebb121c782ad", "url": "https://github.com/apache/kafka/commit/0ba0a4735ecc71d9c335d7ecaffcebb121c782ad", "message": "fix style", "committedDate": "2021-01-28T18:35:47Z", "type": "commit"}]}